Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.30,0:00:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位，卡萊多之星就要開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.40,0:00:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觀看卡萊多之星的時候請保持室內的亮度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.50,0:00:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要離電視太近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.10,0:00:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，那麼，那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.40,0:00:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家有沒有過全力以赴的去做一件事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.00,0:00:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我總是不停對自己說加油！加油！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.80,0:00:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是蕾拉小姐更勝一籌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.50,0:00:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她一直都在努力做的更好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.40,0:00:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們二人的表演一定會\N成功！成功！成功！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.30,0:02:13.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說了你這樣太慢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.10,0:02:16.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，對不起，請再來一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.80,0:02:18.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.30,0:02:19.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像很困難啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.50,0:02:24.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.70,0:02:28.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，是我太快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.70,0:02:32.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE TWO THREE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.20,0:02:34.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.60,0:02:38.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離初演日只有一周的時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.50,0:02:41.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空跟不上節奏，總是太慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.90,0:02:44.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不就是過於緊張而太快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.10,0:03:04.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道卡洛斯在想些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.90,0:03:08.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過你和空始終是格格不入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.10,0:03:09.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太勉強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.80,0:03:14.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡洛斯是個為了製造效果\N不擇手段的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.90,0:03:17.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不覺得你們被他玩弄了麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.60,0:03:20.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真想表演好這出劇目的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.50,0:03:22.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們一定要能好好配合才行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.00,0:03:28.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡洛斯到底在盤算\N些什麼和我沒有關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.20,0:03:30.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.00,0:03:34.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE TWO THREE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.50,0:03:36.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.00,0:03:36.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又掉下去了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.80,0:03:38.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.20,0:03:40.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為總是合不上節拍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.60,0:03:44.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是光看著蕾拉小姐\N的動作就會慢一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.80,0:03:46.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可我又必須得跟上才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.90,0:03:49.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.50,0:03:50.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.70,0:03:51.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有客人來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.60,0:03:54.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,客人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.60,0:03:55.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.10,0:03:59.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.00,0:04:00.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.10,0:04:01.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了，蕾拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.40,0:04:05.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.40,0:04:07.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從今天開始，我會暫時住在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.60,0:04:16.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個……這個是我因為總是跟不上節奏\N所以請健替我拍的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.10,0:04:21.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到這裏來就是為了體會你的步調和節奏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.40,0:04:25.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也請你用你的身體來體會我的步調和節奏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.50,0:04:27.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐的步調和節奏……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.70,0:04:29.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.70,0:04:36.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是……太漂亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.40,0:04:37.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.60,0:04:39.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.70,0:04:44.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼，只是覺得你單脫了上衣好漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.30,0:04:45.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呼吸困難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.50,0:04:50.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們通常是在食堂裏吃晚飯的，蕾拉小姐呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.20,0:04:51.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就一起吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.50,0:04:52.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.40,0:04:53.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吃飯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.70,0:04:56.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.70,0:04:58.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐在……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.30,0:05:01.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，蕾拉小姐暫時會在這裏住一段時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.60,0:05:02.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.70,0:05:06.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個競演啊，我們誰都應該可以勝任的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.10,0:05:09.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛\N要是我的話一定會表演的很完美的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.30,0:05:10.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以輪到我了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.80,0:05:12.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒挑完呢……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.10,0:05:34.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅是走路\N都能感到蕾拉小姐的動作很優雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.80,0:05:39.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫你倒杯咖啡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.70,0:05:42.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用太費心了，我還是先沖澡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.70,0:05:45.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要衝澡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.00,0:05:46.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的要衝澡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.70,0:05:47.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有問題嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.60,0:05:51.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，不，沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.30,0:05:52.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請慢慢使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.30,0:05:59.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以這樣對待我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.30,0:06:01.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過今天我的努力的方向改變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.50,0:06:06.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總是要留神防備可真累啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.10,0:06:13.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.40,0:06:19.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐，你的那身打扮不太妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.20,0:06:20.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.00,0:06:21.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之請換了它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.70,0:06:23.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是換什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.20,0:06:24.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請換這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.50,0:06:26.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.40,0:06:30.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我的屋裏，就請照我的意思做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.90,0:06:32.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.30,0:06:42.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐請睡床上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.30,0:06:44.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我睡地板上好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.30,0:06:46.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了沒有關係麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.00,0:06:48.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.60,0:06:58.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓蕾拉小姐這麼委屈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.40,0:07:00.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果還是不能跟上節奏的話……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.60,0:07:04.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能想這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.30,0:07:06.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要做到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.20,0:07:07.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睡容都是那麼美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.90,0:07:09.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫魯？什麼時候出來的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.70,0:07:12.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我努力的方向改變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.80,0:07:25.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，或許會有意料不到的事發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.90,0:07:29.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐來這裏就是意料不到的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.80,0:07:31.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，的確如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.10,0:07:34.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要吵醒蕾拉小姐哦，夫魯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.10,0:07:45.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐的動作\N蕾拉小姐的節奏、蕾拉小姐的步調
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.70,0:07:50.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得快點……得快點體會才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.40,0:07:52.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關鍵的地方的節奏還是不合拍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.90,0:07:55.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是沒有抓到感覺，還是不合拍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.50,0:07:59.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.60,0:08:00.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.70,0:08:20.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看她們二個好像挺協調了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.30,0:08:21.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空一直都在努力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.20,0:08:29.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經配合的很好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.50,0:08:32.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來到出場的時候應該沒有問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.70,0:08:36.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是\N是否已經達到高潮的那幕要求的演技了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.60,0:09:00.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.80,0:09:02.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跳的太近了，啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.20,0:09:06.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來初演日應該可以按時上演了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.50,0:09:12.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過高潮那幕的難度\N我覺得稍微降低點比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.50,0:09:15.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是說要把高潮一幕改的簡單些？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.40,0:09:21.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，總之陀螺球技的表演這次就取消了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.50,0:09:25.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和新人競演這種難度的表演太冒險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.70,0:09:28.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為導演我也不希望冒這個險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.90,0:09:30.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我可是全力以赴……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.80,0:09:31.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.20,0:09:34.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是已經沒有時間了不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.30,0:09:34.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不同意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.70,0:09:38.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.00,0:09:41.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我決不允許高潮一幕草草了事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.30,0:09:43.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天再給我一天的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.20,0:09:45.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天是初演前的總彩排
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.10,0:09:49.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了等你們大家已經都延遲到明天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.00,0:09:51.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彩排由替補演員頂替
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.60,0:09:53.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的打算這麼辦嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.00,0:09:54.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.30,0:09:55.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝，卡洛斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.40,0:09:58.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.30,0:09:59.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.20,0:10:00.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.20,0:10:02.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說要打個電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.70,0:10:03.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.70,0:10:04.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.90,0:10:08.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，爭取到明天最後一天的練習時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.60,0:10:10.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎，那太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.10,0:10:11.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝，那麼我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.60,0:10:16.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空，你一定行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.90,0:10:28.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好，準備的怎麼樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.40,0:10:30.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好啊，小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.60,0:10:32.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒有問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.40,0:10:33.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.20,0:10:33.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.00,0:10:36.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點上船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.60,0:10:37.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.10,0:10:40.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來天氣真不錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.60,0:10:41.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.50,0:10:45.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天氣……不錯嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.50,0:10:51.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.70,0:10:52.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始進行特訓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.90,0:11:10.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易剛剛才能合拍的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.10,0:11:13.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在真正的海上能行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.70,0:11:17.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前我們的練習全部都要忘記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.00,0:11:22.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到目前為止\N我也一直努力於我們之間的配合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.20,0:11:24.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是一直這樣重複下去\N即使能夠做到配合的很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.40,0:11:27.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也只能演出一場無聊的表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.10,0:11:28.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.40,0:11:31.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始是我和你的真正的決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.70,0:11:34.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和蕾拉小姐的真正的決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.60,0:11:36.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.00,0:11:37.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接受嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.80,0:11:38.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.90,0:11:42.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要系安全帶嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.60,0:11:45.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就不用了，會妨礙我的行動的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.20,0:11:46.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.50,0:11:46.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.00,0:11:56.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在看到的是真正的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.90,0:12:33.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好強勁的氣勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.60,0:12:37.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍不留神就會真的掉進海裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.20,0:12:39.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疏忽大意的話可是會成為魚餌的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.20,0:12:56.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真正的海上\N連蕾拉小姐也不可預料的動作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.30,0:13:06.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，是的，現在應該在海上特訓吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.10,0:13:08.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,預行演習請照舊進行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.50,0:13:10.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初演日可以照日程安排開幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.20,0:13:18.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉，還沒輪到你出場呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.00,0:13:20.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧，對不起啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.50,0:13:23.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對對，前後的距離都看好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.40,0:13:26.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,李可，那邊向前移動一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.80,0:13:27.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.90,0:13:29.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特訓？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.30,0:13:32.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天就是初演日了，不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.30,0:13:35.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道蕾拉小姐怎麼想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.60,0:13:37.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我還是很擔心這個天氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.00,0:13:51.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太厲害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.40,0:14:17.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就快到……極限了麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.00,0:14:19.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.80,0:14:36.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要這麼叫啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.10,0:14:38.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之你們站在那裏就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.20,0:14:38.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.80,0:14:43.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天的初演真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.50,0:15:05.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.20,0:15:17.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺還行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.60,0:15:21.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.50,0:15:30.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,風雨還是很大\N我們只能在這裏呆到明天早上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.60,0:15:31.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.30,0:15:34.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天就是正式演出了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.20,0:15:37.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正式演出……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.40,0:15:38.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.10,0:15:41.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正式演出時能下雨嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.80,0:15:46.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐果然很厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.70,0:15:49.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論什麼時候都在考慮演出的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.80,0:15:58.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐為什麼\N會進入卡萊多劇團的呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.10,0:16:03.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小的時候和父母\N一起去看過卡萊多的表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.30,0:16:06.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那次的表演象夢幻一般的精彩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.00,0:16:10.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然劇目還是那個劇目\N不過父母卻象孩子一樣的笑著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.40,0:16:14.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我覺得不可思議的驚奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.10,0:16:15.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是哪個劇目呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.30,0:16:18.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綠野仙蹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.40,0:16:21.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綠野仙蹤？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.00,0:16:37.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和過世的父母一起\N看的那個劇目也是綠野仙蹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.10,0:16:43.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過那件事是我記憶中\N最後一次和父母一起出門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.20,0:16:47.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的母親雖然也過世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.10,0:16:53.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過母親當時又吃驚又開心的表情\N是我第一次也是最後一次看到的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.80,0:17:03.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,母親過世後\N父親因為過於寂寞而整日埋首公務中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.50,0:17:11.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次的表演，你父親要是能來看就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.20,0:17:14.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，是我說了什麼多嘴的話嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.80,0:17:18.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.40,0:17:20.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是第一次和人這麼談心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.10,0:17:26.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個女孩或許真的擁有改變周圍的人的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.20,0:17:31.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個女孩或許真的擁有\N改變周圍的人的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.80,0:17:35.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微休息會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.30,0:17:36.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.10,0:17:39.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說起來，你經常說夢話啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.60,0:17:42.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.50,0:17:45.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢話？應該是指和夫魯說的話吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.40,0:17:53.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不……不會吧？\N今晚她們二個都不能回來了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.10,0:17:55.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在外寄宿了？沒聽說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.60,0:18:00.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然發生了意料之外的事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.30,0:18:05.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.80,0:18:07.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有再等一個晚上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.00,0:18:11.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天你們二個都要回來哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.60,0:18:20.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.70,0:18:23.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.30,0:18:23.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.00,0:18:29.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我 初演日開幕時間照常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.60,0:18:32.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直接到會場去接蕾拉和空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.50,0:18:35.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.00,0:18:39.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，終於趕上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.50,0:18:51.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.70,0:19:05.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.20,0:19:06.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎歸來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.80,0:19:12.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.70,0:19:17.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬，我想要雨景效果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.20,0:19:20.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雨景？知道了，我盡力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.30,0:19:21.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家過來一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.40,0:19:23.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎你回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.70,0:19:24.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.90,0:20:05.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.20,0:20:23.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.50,0:20:25.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,火焰已經準備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.90,0:20:27.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，點火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.30,0:20:28.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,點火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.10,0:21:01.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.00,0:21:09.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.10,0:21:43.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種感覺真是久違了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.40,0:21:45.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.00,0:21:48.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我……好開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.60,0:21:51.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道該怎麼說好，但是好開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.80,0:23:22.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集預告：卡萊多之星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.10,0:23:24.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只會按照劇本演出太幼稚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.40,0:23:25.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.80,0:23:29.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難得有休息的機會，卻只有我要工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.80,0:23:31.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是去別的劇團友情出演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.80,0:23:33.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會陪你去的，加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.20,0:23:35.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是一個不同的試煉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.30,0:23:38.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一波未平一波又起！起！起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.80,0:23:40.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一集卡萊多之星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.30,0:23:45.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翅膀是夢想，飛向空
